{"title":"Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境","uid":"763d136eb7a9aabb3a0905fee9df0a87","slug":"Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境","date":"2022-01-20T05:30:23.000Z","updated":"2022-01-21T05:50:27.334Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://www.egehangundogdu.com/stupheem/2019/01/virtualenv.jpeg","content":"<h1 id=\"Ubuntu-創建-Python-虛擬環境\"><a href=\"#Ubuntu-創建-Python-虛擬環境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境\"></a>Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境</h1><h2 id=\"step\"><a href=\"#step\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"step\"></a>step</h2><ol>\n<li>安裝 virtualenv (以 Python3 為例)<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> python3-pip\n$ pip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> virtualenv<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p>或</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> python3-virtualenv<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>建立虛擬環境</li>\n</ol>\n<p>建立前要先知道你想使用的 Python 版本放在哪，假設我想使用 Python3</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">which</span> python3<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>得到路徑後使用以下指令建立</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ virtualenv -p <span class=\"token variable\">$python</span>路徑 $想創建的環境名稱<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>啟動虛擬環境<br>建立後可以在目錄發現多了一個環境名稱的資料夾，在終端機中進去 source activate 這個檔案即可啟動虛擬環境<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> $環境名稱/bin/activate<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p>成功後會看到終端機名稱前方出現 (&lt;環境名稱&gt;)，如下</p>\n<p>(&lt;環境名稱&gt;)$ </p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><p>離開虛擬環境</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>環境名稱<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>$ deactivate<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>其他指令<br>可使用 pip install 安裝虛擬環境內所需套件</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","feature":true,"text":"Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境step 安裝 virtualenv (以 Python3 為例)$ sudo apt-get install python3-pip $ pip3 install virtualenv 或 $ sudo apt install pyth...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":486,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Ubuntu","slug":"Ubuntu","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Ubuntu.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"system","slug":"system","count":2,"path":"api/tags/system.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Ubuntu-%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA-Python-%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Ubuntu 創建 Python 虛擬環境</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#step\"><span class=\"toc-text\">step</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Siang Wei","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.imgur.com/JOzonsP.jpg","link":"/","description":"隨心所欲，由心而生的技術人","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/wimterdom","twitter":"https://twitter.com/wimterdom","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","